    <p>Archive content licensed under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CC BY-SA 4.0</a> unless otherwise noted. Video licenses remain with their respective owners.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
